<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 4" captionStartId="F4" captionText="Figure 4. Cestrum darienense A. K. Monro A Flowering stem B Style C Longitudinal section through the corolla showing stamen arrangement D Flower. Drawn from J. P. Folsom, R. L. Hartman &amp; R. L. Dressler 4415 (MO)." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/9972" pageId="8" pageNumber="57">Fig. 4 A-D</figureCitation>
